---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Apex Web Solutions"
  description="Read the Privacy Policy for Apex Web Solutions. Learn how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information while using our web design services."
>
  <div class="bg-background min-h-screen pt-24 pb-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8 text-sm">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p>
          At Apex Web Solutions, we are committed to protecting your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your
          information when you visit our website or use our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us
          when you:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Fill out a contact form</li>
          <li>Subscribe to our newsletter</li>
          <li>Request a quote or service</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          This information may include your name, email address, phone number,
          and company details.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
          <li>Communicate with you regarding updates or inquiries</li>
          <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Data Protection</h2>
        <p>
          We implement industry-standard security measures to maintain the
          safety of your personal information. However, no method of
          transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may strictly use trusted third-party services for analytics,
          hosting, and payment processing. These parties are obligated to keep
          your information confidential.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us
          at:
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium">
          Email: <a
            href="mailto:info@apexwebsolutions.com"
            class="text-primary hover:underline">info@apexwebsolutions.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
